                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2209" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0343</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8876 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易成公司：国业改制后如何进行企业文化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yi Cheng: How to transform the Corporate Culture when state-owned enterprise remanufacture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鲁云，曲丽伟等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易成新材料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业；改制；企业文化；转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">state-owned enterprise;remanufacture;Corporate Culture;transform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当前，为了改变国有资产严重流失、国企运营效益低下等弊病；我国政府正在致力于推进国有企业的改制工作，传统国企纷纷向现代股份企业开始转型。而这种转型不但体现在经营管理体制和机制的转变上，也必然体现到企业文化的转变上。优秀的企业文化，作为企业精神的内涵，以共有的价值观念为基石，进而形成企业的制度，规范企业的行为，塑造企业的风格。2010年，平顶山易成新材料股份有限公司(以下简称“易成公司”)改制后，对业务、治理结构、财务等方面进行了一系列改革与重组，将组织形式变更为股份有限公司。在股份改制后，易成就将面临投资主体多元化、相关利益多方化和员工成分多样化等问题。如何解决这些问题，使得各方和全体员工的思想和行为相协调？如何促进改制之后企业各部门的合作，使企业文化与企业经营理念、发展战略相匹配？易成公司为了使得在改制之后企业更好的发展，决定大力促进公司企业文化的转型，并提出相关的配套措施方案。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At present, the Chinese government is committed to advancing the restructuring work of state-owned enterprises. To change serious loss of state assets, low efficiency of operations and other ills, the traditional state-owned enterprises have begun to transform themselves to modern joint-stock companies. And this transformation is not only reflected in the management system and mechanisms of business, but also to the corporate culture. As a company’s spiritual content, excellent corporate culture which based on shared values, involved in the formation of enterprise system, standardization of enterprise behavior, shaping of the style of business. 2010，With YICHENG new material Co.,Ltd  remanufacturing, it also makes a series of reform and reorganization, like the business, governance structure, financial, etc. After the transformation ,YICHENG will face a lot of problems, such as the diversity of ownership system and operation ,etc. How to solve these problems, make the parties and all the staff in harmony? ?How to promote each department cooperation, transform enterprise culture to match with the development strategy? YICHENG want to make a big progress after remanufacturing ,so decide to transform the corporate culture and put forward the relevant supporting measures.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化建立及转变</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-10</td>
                            </tr>
